## Quick Reference

```bash
# Local development
just up                     # Start ops + app
just up-all                 # Start all (+ caddy, promtail, watchtower, vault-agent)
just down                   # Stop all
just logs                   # View logs
just ps                     # Show containers
{% if use_terraform %}

# Terraform
just tf-init dev
just tf-plan dev
just tf-apply dev
{% endif %}
{% if vault %}

# Vault
just vault-init             # First time setup
just vault-unseal           # Run 3x with different keys
just vault-put local {{ service_name }} KEY=value
{% endif %}

# Linting
just lint                   # Run all checks
```

